      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="24053964">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/meijiahe/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4291162-74.jpg" alt="吃饱了撑着才" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/24053964/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/24053964/" class="">第74页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/meijiahe/" class=" " title="吃饱了撑着才">吃饱了撑着才</a>
                (抱朴持中 心火不灭)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="24053964">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">我们对世界的原初理解并非把事物理解为客体，而是理解为希腊人所谓的处境（pragmata）。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-01-21 10:01</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>我们对世界的原初理解并非把事物理解为客体，而是理解为希腊人所谓的处境（pragmata）。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

